{
  "video_id": "H03o2WCBoDU",
  "title": "The real reason manufacturing jobs are disappearing | Augie Picado",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12700.0,
      "end_time": 14395.0,
      "text": "When someone mentions Cuba,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14420.0,
      "end_time": 15620.0,
      "text": "what do you think about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17200.0,
      "end_time": 19760.0,
      "text": "Classic, classic cars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19100.0,
      "end_time": 20420.0,
      "text": "Perhaps good cigars?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21420.0,
      "end_time": 23516.0,
      "text": "Maybe you think of a famous baseball player."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23540.0,
      "end_time": 25875.0,
      "text": "What about when somebody mentions North Korea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25900.0,
      "end_time": 27994.0,
      "text": "You think about those missile tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28200.0,
      "end_time": 29916.0,
      "text": "maybe their notorious leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29940.0,
      "end_time": 31940.0,
      "text": "or his good friend, Dennis Rodman."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32460.0,
      "end_time": 33956.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33980.0,
      "end_time": 36315.0,
      "text": "One thing that likely doesn&#39;t come to mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36340.0,
      "end_time": 38100.0,
      "text": "is a vision of a country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38780.0,
      "end_time": 40360.0,
      "text": "an open economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40600.0,
      "end_time": 44579.0,
      "text": "whose citizens have access to a wide range of affordable consumer products."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47600.0,
      "end_time": 51676.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not here to argue how these countries got to where they are today."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51700.0,
      "end_time": 55396.0,
      "text": "I simply want to use them as an example of countries and citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55420.0,
      "end_time": 58636.0,
      "text": "who have been affected, negatively affected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58660.0,
      "end_time": 60940.0,
      "text": "by a trade policy that restricts imports"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61780.0,
      "end_time": 63300.0,
      "text": "and protects local industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64300.0,
      "end_time": 67196.0,
      "text": "Recently we&#39;ve heard a number of countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67220.0,
      "end_time": 69396.0,
      "text": "talk about restricting imports"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69420.0,
      "end_time": 72436.0,
      "text": "and protecting their local, domestic industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72460.0,
      "end_time": 75716.0,
      "text": "Now, this may sound fine in a sound bite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75740.0,
      "end_time": 77979.0,
      "text": "but what it really is is protectionism."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78980.0,
      "end_time": 82740.0,
      "text": "We heard a lot about this during the 2016 presidential election."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83420.0,
      "end_time": 85876.0,
      "text": "We heard about it during the Brexit debates"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85900.0,
      "end_time": 89220.0,
      "text": "and most recently during the French elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90500.0,
      "end_time": 93236.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s been a really important topic"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 95396.0,
      "text": "being talked about around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95420.0,
      "end_time": 97836.0,
      "text": "and many aspiring political leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97860.0,
      "end_time": 101420.0,
      "text": "are running on platforms positioning protectionism as a good thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102620.0,
      "end_time": 105396.0,
      "text": "Now, I could see why they think protectionism is good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105420.0,
      "end_time": 109540.0,
      "text": "because sometimes it seems like trade is unfair."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110940.0,
      "end_time": 112876.0,
      "text": "Some have blamed trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112900.0,
      "end_time": 116360.0,
      "text": "for some of the problems we&#39;ve been having here at home in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116600.0,
      "end_time": 117436.0,
      "text": "For years we&#39;ve been hearing"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117460.0,
      "end_time": 120660.0,
      "text": "about the loss of high-paying US manufacturing jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121380.0,
      "end_time": 124955.0,
      "text": "Many think that manufacturing is declining in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124980.0,
      "end_time": 128116.0,
      "text": "because companies are moving their operations offshore"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128139.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130555.00000000001,
      "text": "to markets with lower-cost labor"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130580.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133140.0,
      "text": "like China, Mexico and Vietnam."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134540.0,
      "end_time": 138196.0,
      "text": "They also think trade agreements sometimes are unfair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138220.0,
      "end_time": 139916.0,
      "text": "like NAFTA"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139940.0,
      "end_time": 141756.0,
      "text": "and the Trans-Pacific Partnership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141780.0,
      "end_time": 145236.0,
      "text": "because these trade agreements allow companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148500.0,
      "text": "to reimport those cheaply produced goods back into the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149540.0,
      "end_time": 152676.0,
      "text": "and other countries from where the jobs were taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152700.0,
      "end_time": 155796.0,
      "text": "So it kind of feels like the exporters win"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155820.0,
      "end_time": 157820.0,
      "text": "and the importers lose."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158780.0,
      "end_time": 159996.0,
      "text": "Now, the reality is"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 160200.0,
      "end_time": 162940.0,
      "text": "output in the manufacturing sector in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163900.0,
      "end_time": 165636.0,
      "text": "is actually growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165660.0,
      "end_time": 167236.0,
      "text": "but we are losing jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 168500.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re losing lots of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169220.0,
      "end_time": 171916.0,
      "text": "In fact, from 2000 to 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171940.0,
      "end_time": 175579.0,
      "text": "5.7 million manufacturing jobs were lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176380.0,
      "end_time": 179940.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re not being lost for the reasons you might think."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 180940.0,
      "end_time": 182780.0,
      "text": "Mike Johnson in Toledo, Ohio"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183900.0,
      "end_time": 185876.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t lose his jobs at the factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185900.0,
      "end_time": 188356.0,
      "text": "to Miguel Sanchez in Monterrey, Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188380.0,
      "end_time": 189596.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189620.0,
      "end_time": 191900.0,
      "text": "Mike lost his job to a machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193420.0,
      "end_time": 196715.0,
      "text": "87 percent of lost manufacturing jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196740.0,
      "end_time": 199556.0,
      "text": "have been eliminated because we&#39;ve made improvements"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 199580.0,
      "end_time": 202140.0,
      "text": "in our own productivity through automation."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203540.0,
      "end_time": 208236.0,
      "text": "So that means that one out of 10 lost manufacturing jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210540.0,
      "text": "was due to offshoring."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 211500.0,
      "end_time": 213916.0,
      "text": "Now, this is not just a US phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213940.0,
      "end_time": 215156.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215180.0,
      "end_time": 218516.0,
      "text": "In fact, automation is spreading to every production line"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218540.0,
      "end_time": 220459.0,
      "text": "in every country around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 221540.0,
      "end_time": 223156.0,
      "text": "But look, I get it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223180.0,
      "end_time": 224676.0,
      "text": "if you just lost your job"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224700.0,
      "end_time": 226356.0,
      "text": "and then you read in the newspaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226380.0,
      "end_time": 228996.0,
      "text": "that your old company just struck up a deal with China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229200.0,
      "end_time": 231476.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easy to think you were just replaced"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231500.0,
      "end_time": 232700.0,
      "text": "in a one-for-one deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 233900.0,
      "end_time": 236876.0,
      "text": "When I hear stories like this, I think that what people picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 236900.0,
      "end_time": 240180.0,
      "text": "is that trade happens between only two countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240940.0,
      "end_time": 243356.0,
      "text": "Manufacturers in one country"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 243380.0,
      "end_time": 245316.0,
      "text": "produce products and they export them"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245340.0,
      "end_time": 247980.0,
      "text": "to consumers in other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 248820.0,
      "end_time": 251835.0,
      "text": "and it feels like the manufacturing countries win"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 251860.0,
      "end_time": 254420.0,
      "text": "and the importing countries lose."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 255340.0,
      "end_time": 257860.0,
      "text": "Well, reality&#39;s a little bit different."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 259220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260796.00000000003,
      "text": "I&#39;m a supply chain professional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 260820.0,
      "end_time": 262580.0,
      "text": "and I live and work in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 264340.0,
      "end_time": 265595.0,
      "text": "And I work in the middle"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 265620.0,
      "end_time": 268796.0,
      "text": "of a highly connected network of manufacturers"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268820.0,
      "end_time": 270956.0,
      "text": "all collaborating from around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270980.0,
      "end_time": 273380.0,
      "text": "to produce many of the products we use today."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274420.0,
      "end_time": 275636.0,
      "text": "What I see"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275660.0,
      "end_time": 278236.0,
      "text": "from my front-row seat in Mexico City"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280580.0,
      "text": "actually looks more like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 281500.0,
      "end_time": 285580.0,
      "text": "And this is a more accurate depiction of what trade really looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 286436.0,
      "end_time": 288436.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had the pleasure of being able to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 288460.0,
      "end_time": 290955.0,
      "text": "how many different products are manufactured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 290980.0,
      "end_time": 293796.0,
      "text": "from golf clubs to laptop computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 293820.0,
      "end_time": 296396.0,
      "text": "to internet servers, automobiles"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 296420.0,
      "end_time": 297620.0,
      "text": "and even airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 298340.0,
      "end_time": 301990.0,
      "text": "And believe me, none of it happens in a straight line."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 303546.0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 305340.0,
      "end_time": 309596.0,
      "text": "A few months ago, I was touring the manufacturing plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309620.0,
      "end_time": 312596.0,
      "text": "of a multinational aerospace company"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 312620.0,
      "end_time": 313900.0,
      "text": "in Querétaro, Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 314740.0,
      "end_time": 318300.0,
      "text": "and the VP of logistics points out a completed tail assembly."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 323635.0,
      "text": "It turns out the tail assemblies are assembled from panels"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 323660.0,
      "end_time": 326156.0,
      "text": "that are manufactured in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 326180.0,
      "end_time": 328396.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re assembled in Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328420.0,
      "end_time": 331340.0,
      "text": "using components imported from the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 331860.0,
      "end_time": 333876.0,
      "text": "When those tail assemblies are done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 333900.0,
      "end_time": 336356.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re exported via truck to Canada"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336380.0,
      "end_time": 338556.0,
      "text": "to their primary assembly plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 338580.0,
      "end_time": 339835.0,
      "text": "where they come together"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 339860.0,
      "end_time": 342276.0,
      "text": "with thousands of other parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 342300.0,
      "end_time": 344676.0,
      "text": "like the wings and the seats"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 344700.0,
      "end_time": 347596.0,
      "text": "and the little shades over the little windows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 347620.0,
      "end_time": 350200.0,
      "text": "all coming in to become a part of a new airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 351300.0,
      "end_time": 352500.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 353140.0,
      "end_time": 354596.0,
      "text": "These new airplanes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 354620.0,
      "end_time": 357196.0,
      "text": "before they even take their first flight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 357220.0,
      "end_time": 359676.0,
      "text": "they have more stamps in their passports"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 359700.0,
      "end_time": 360940.0,
      "text": "than Angelina Jolie."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 362580.0,
      "end_time": 366750.0,
      "text": "Now, this approach to processing goes on all around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 366100.0,
      "end_time": 368596.0,
      "text": "to manufacture many of the products"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 368620.0,
      "end_time": 371156.0,
      "text": "we use every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 371180.0,
      "end_time": 373500.0,
      "text": "from skin cream to airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374340.0,
      "end_time": 376780.0,
      "text": "When you go home tonight, take a look in your house."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377500.0,
      "end_time": 380700.0,
      "text": "You might be surprised to find a label that looks like this one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 381900.0,
      "end_time": 386990.0,
      "text": "\"Manufactured in the USA from US and foreign parts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 386980.0,
      "end_time": 389156.0,
      "text": "Economist Michael Porter"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 389180.0,
      "end_time": 391140.0,
      "text": "described what&#39;s going on here best."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 391660.0,
      "end_time": 396396.0,
      "text": "Many decades ago, he said that it&#39;s most beneficial for a country"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 396420.0,
      "end_time": 400796.0,
      "text": "to focus on producing the products it can produce most efficiently"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 400820.0,
      "end_time": 402580.0,
      "text": "and trading for the rest."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 403820.0,
      "end_time": 406580.0,
      "text": "So what he&#39;s talking about here is shared production,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 407340.0,
      "end_time": 409219.0,
      "text": "and efficiency is the name of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 410540.0,
      "end_time": 413760.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve probably seen an example of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 413100.0,
      "end_time": 414460.0,
      "text": "at home or at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 415620.0,
      "end_time": 417356.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 417380.0,
      "end_time": 419500.0,
      "text": "Think about how your house was built"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 420340.0,
      "end_time": 421739.0,
      "text": "or your kitchen renovated."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 422420.0,
      "end_time": 424876.0,
      "text": "Typically, there&#39;s a general contractor"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 424900.0,
      "end_time": 427116.0,
      "text": "who is responsible for coordinating the efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 427140.0,
      "end_time": 428756.0,
      "text": "of all the different contractors:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 428780.0,
      "end_time": 430419.0,
      "text": "an architect to draw the plans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 431300.0,
      "end_time": 434236.0,
      "text": "an earth-moving company to dig the foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436140.0,
      "text": "a plumber, a carpenter and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 436820.0,
      "end_time": 438676.0,
      "text": "So why doesn&#39;t the general contractor"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 438700.0,
      "end_time": 441316.0,
      "text": "pick just one company"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 441340.0,
      "end_time": 442556.0,
      "text": "to do all the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 442580.0,
      "end_time": 443780.0,
      "text": "like, say, the architect?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 444420.0,
      "end_time": 445620.0,
      "text": "Because this is silly."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446580.0,
      "end_time": 448876.0,
      "text": "The general contractor selects experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448900.0,
      "end_time": 450635.0,
      "text": "because it takes years"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 450660.0,
      "end_time": 452396.0,
      "text": "to learn and master"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 452420.0,
      "end_time": 456196.0,
      "text": "how to do each of the tasks it takes to build a house or renovate a kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 456220.0,
      "end_time": 458500.0,
      "text": "some of them requiring special training."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 459860.0,
      "end_time": 461760.0,
      "text": "Think about it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 461100.0,
      "end_time": 464540.0,
      "text": "Would you want your architect to install your toilet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 465140.0,
      "end_time": 466556.0,
      "text": "Of course not."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 466580.0,
      "end_time": 469419.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s apply this process to the corporate world."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 470200.0,
      "end_time": 472596.0,
      "text": "Companies today focus on manufacturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 472620.0,
      "end_time": 475956.0,
      "text": "what they produce best and most efficiently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 475980.0,
      "end_time": 477820.0,
      "text": "and they trade for everything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 478500.0,
      "end_time": 481196.0,
      "text": "So this means they rely"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 481220.0,
      "end_time": 486196.0,
      "text": "on a global, interconnected, interdependent network of manufacturers"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 486220.0,
      "end_time": 487476.0,
      "text": "to produce these products."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 487500.0,
      "end_time": 489556.0,
      "text": "In fact, that network is so interconnected"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 489580.0,
      "end_time": 490820.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s almost impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 491900.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "to dismantle and produce products in just one country."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 495940.0,
      "end_time": 498236.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a look at the interconnected web"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 499916.0,
      "text": "we saw a few moments ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 499940.0,
      "end_time": 502236.0,
      "text": "and let&#39;s focus on just one strand"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 504340.0,
      "text": "between the US and Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 506460.0,
      "end_time": 509275.0,
      "text": "The Wilson Institute says that shared production represents"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 509300.0,
      "end_time": 514380.0,
      "text": "40 percent of the half a trillion dollars in trade between the US and Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 514900.0,
      "end_time": 517555.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s about 200 billion dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 517580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520540.00000000006,
      "text": "or the same as the GDP for Portugal."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 521539.0,
      "end_time": 524750.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s just imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 524100.0,
      "end_time": 527196.0,
      "text": "that the US decides to impose"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 527220.0,
      "end_time": 530940.0,
      "text": "a 20 percent border tax on all imports from Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 531660.0,
      "end_time": 532876.0,
      "text": "OK, fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 532900.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "But do you think Mexico is just going to stand by and let that happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 537940.0,
      "end_time": 539636.0,
      "text": "No. No way."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 539660.0,
      "end_time": 542716.0,
      "text": "So in retaliation, they impose a similar tax"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 542740.0,
      "end_time": 545580.0,
      "text": "on all goods being imported from the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 546460.0,
      "end_time": 548700.0,
      "text": "and a little game of tit-for-tat ensues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 550200.0,
      "end_time": 553476.0,
      "text": "and 20 percent -- just imagine that 20 percent duties"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 553500.0,
      "end_time": 556996.0,
      "text": "are added to every good, product, product component"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 557200.0,
      "end_time": 559716.0,
      "text": "crossing back and forth across the border,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 559740.0,
      "end_time": 563760.0,
      "text": "and you could be looking at more than a 40 percent increase in duties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 563100.0,
      "end_time": 564860.0,
      "text": "or 80 billion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 565620.0,
      "end_time": 567396.0,
      "text": "Now, don&#39;t kid yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 567420.0,
      "end_time": 569716.0,
      "text": "these costs are going to be passed along"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 569740.0,
      "end_time": 571980.0,
      "text": "to you and to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 573780.0,
      "end_time": 579360.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s think about what impact that might have on some of the products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 579600.0,
      "end_time": 581780.0,
      "text": "or the prices of the products, that we buy every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 582420.0,
      "end_time": 586836.0,
      "text": "So if a 30 percent increase in duties were actually passed along,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 586860.0,
      "end_time": 590500.0,
      "text": "we would be looking at some pretty important increases in prices."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 591460.0,
      "end_time": 595260.0,
      "text": "A Lincoln MKZ would go from 37,000 dollars to 48,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 596580.0,
      "end_time": 599940.0,
      "text": "And the price of a Sharp 60-inch HDTV"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 600620.0,
      "end_time": 605836.0,
      "text": "would go from 898 dollars to 1,167 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 605860.0,
      "end_time": 609996.0,
      "text": "And the price of a 16-ounce jar of CVS skin moisturizer"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 610200.0,
      "end_time": 613460.0,
      "text": "would go from 13 dollars to 17 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 614600.0,
      "end_time": 619435.0,
      "text": "Now, remember, this is only looking at one strand of the production chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 619460.0,
      "end_time": 620836.0,
      "text": "between the US and Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 620860.0,
      "end_time": 623660.0,
      "text": "so multiply this out across all of the strands."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 624420.0,
      "end_time": 626750.0,
      "text": "The impact could be considerable."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 626100.0,
      "end_time": 628756.0,
      "text": "Now, just think about this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 628780.0,
      "end_time": 632200.0,
      "text": "even if we were able to dismantle this network"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 633300.0,
      "end_time": 636516.0,
      "text": "and produce products in just one country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 636540.0,
      "end_time": 639360.0,
      "text": "which by the way is easier said than done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 639600.0,
      "end_time": 642476.0,
      "text": "we would still only be saving or protecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 642500.0,
      "end_time": 645396.0,
      "text": "one out of 10 lost manufacturing jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 645420.0,
      "end_time": 647459.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right, because remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 649220.0,
      "end_time": 651876.0,
      "text": "most of those jobs, 87 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 651900.0,
      "end_time": 654579.0,
      "text": "were lost due to improvements in our own productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 655340.0,
      "end_time": 658500.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, those jobs, they&#39;re gone for good."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 659980.0,
      "end_time": 661540.0,
      "text": "So the real question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 662340.0,
      "end_time": 664676.0,
      "text": "does it make sense for us to drive up prices"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 664700.0,
      "end_time": 670220.0,
      "text": "to the point where many of us can&#39;t afford the basic goods we use every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 671100.0,
      "end_time": 673316.0,
      "text": "for the purpose of saving a job"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 673340.0,
      "end_time": 675820.0,
      "text": "that might be eliminated in a couple of years anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 677860.0,
      "end_time": 679876.0,
      "text": "The reality is that shared production"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 679900.0,
      "end_time": 683555.0,
      "text": "allows us to manufacture higher quality products"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 683580.0,
      "end_time": 684796.0,
      "text": "at lower costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 684820.0,
      "end_time": 686200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s that simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 686780.0,
      "end_time": 688636.0,
      "text": "It allows us to get more"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 688660.0,
      "end_time": 691760.0,
      "text": "out of the limited resources and expertise we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 691100.0,
      "end_time": 694300.0,
      "text": "and at the same time benefit from lower prices."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 695380.0,
      "end_time": 697436.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really important to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 697460.0,
      "end_time": 700276.0,
      "text": "that for shared production to be effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 700300.0,
      "end_time": 705716.0,
      "text": "it relies on efficient cross-border movement of raw materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 705740.0,
      "end_time": 707700.0,
      "text": "components and finished products."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 708780.0,
      "end_time": 709980.0,
      "text": "So remember this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 710940.0,
      "end_time": 714996.0,
      "text": "the next time you&#39;re hearing somebody try to sell you on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 715200.0,
      "end_time": 717340.0,
      "text": "that protectionism is a good deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 718260.0,
      "end_time": 719836.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just not."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 719860.0,
      "end_time": 721760.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 721100.0,
      "end_time": 723860.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}